<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>List of Nigerian Institutions</title>

  <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->
  <meta name="description" content="Discover a comprehensive list of Nigerian educational institutions including universities, polytechnics, and colleges. Filter institutions by category and learn more.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="Nigerian institutions, universities in Nigeria, polytechnics in Nigeria, colleges in Nigeria, Nigerian education, school list, education portal">
  <meta name="author" content="Your Name or Website Name">

  <!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="List of Nigerian Institutions">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Browse a categorized list of Nigerian educational institutions. View universities, colleges, and polytechnics in one place.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="mysearch-query.onrender">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://mysearch-query.onrender.com/nigerian-institutions">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://mysearch-query.onrender.com/images/nigerian-schools.jpg">

  <!-- Twitter Card -->
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="List of Nigerian Institutions">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Explore Nigerian universities, polytechnics, and colleges with detailed categorization and selection options.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://mysearch-query.onrender.com/images/nigerian-schools-twitter.jpg">


<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  
  <script>
    function showList(value) {
      const lists = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-list');
      lists.forEach(list => list.style.display = 'none');

      const selected = document.getElementById(value);
      if (selected) {
        selected.style.display = 'block';
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../includeFolder/_headers.ejs') %>
     
    <br>
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px; width:100%; margin:0 auto; padding:clamp(12px, 4vw, 24px); box-sizing:border-box;">

  <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.1rem, 4vw, 1.5rem); margin:0 0 0.6rem 0; color:#2c3e50; line-height:1.3;">
    Select Institution Type
  </h2>

  <p style="font-size:clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1rem); line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 1rem 0; color:#333;">
    Choose whether you want to browse Federal Universities, State Universities, or Polytechnics.
    Picking a category filters the list below to just that type — so instead of scrolling through
    every Nigerian institution at once, you can jump straight to the group you're interested in,
    then use the search box to narrow it down further by name or abbreviation (e.g. "UNILAG" or "LASU").
  </p>

  <ul style="font-size:clamp(0.85rem, 2.3vw, 0.95rem); line-height:1.6; padding-left:1.2rem; margin:0; color:#444;">
    <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;"><strong>Plainer/functional:</strong> "Pick a category to filter the list below — Federal, State, or Polytechnic."</li>
    <li><strong>More promotional:</strong> "Not sure where to start? Filter by institution type first, then search by name to find exactly the school you're looking for."</li>
  </ul>

</div>

<br>

